Date    Mon Apr 17 19:03:30 2000~
Stamp   956016210
To      Juwen~
Subject Recruitment, part 1~
Text
I exit the shuttle and walk to HQ. Today is a particularly special day.
Today is the day we get the new recruits. And the rules are quite simple.
If you don't make, you don't leave the base alive. Quite simple. I walk through
the main doors and walk to the barracks. It's always nice to give recruits a rude
awakening. I smile to myself as I shout out orders to the semi-wake men. Only one
seems to be awake. A young drow by the name of Juwen. He seems quite promising. I
do hope he makes it. I led them out to the practice yard and instructed them in the
use of blades. Most of them seemed to be quite good at it. The others won't live
through the night. I don't really enjoy that part, but it's part of the job.
Last night we had a perimeter breach. One of the trainees who were
scheduled for termination tried to scale the gate. I felt confident in Juwen,
And I sent him off to dispose of the coward. He returned in several minutes, his blade
coated in blood and the runners head dangling in his hand. Juwen has great skill and
only needs the proper training to be a highly efficient killer, like my previous students.


(To be continued...)
~
