How can people love? Love is so precious, so rare between two people...
How can people love? Every minute of the day, someone dies. Regardless of how, be it by hunger,
Plague,
Abuse,
Or homicide... how can people love?
I do not understand these factors, for my past brings these out...
How can people love? The can be ripped apart at any time...now..or withing minutes...
<begins to develope a small tear in his eye...>
I know how it feels to be deprived of the things you love within a heartbeat...my house, my homeland,...
I shall stop hear. <Seems to be emotionless, but you can see right through to his sorrow...>
