Subject The Chosen Go Forth~
Text
``   Several days after the attack on the queen, the holders of the letters from the seraphim, Dhonivan, put
their sets on finding the queen and guarding her, while a team will go out to find the hideout of the replacement
killers. Their objective:
``             `!-`&Find out why the assassins were sent after the Queen.
``             `!-`&Find out who leads them.``
``             `!-`&And destroy them, if nessicary.``

``   As a small group will be left behind to guard the queen, Tyronos shall lead the rest of the party on the
raid. But there are still many questions brewing in his mind. Why were they chosen by Serraph? What is their
purpose in all of this? What is to come on the horizon that the seraphim speaks of as 'The End'?

[`&Onward!``]
~
Sender  Ethera~
Date    Thu Aug 10 01:58:07 2000~
Stamp   965890687
To      thaais rinako~
Subject Little adventure.~
Text
Ethera sits behind her desk, in the office of Black Flag Investments. She looks over the financial reports and shakes her head, sighing.
`^Idiots..i'm surrounded by them. Them and freaks.'`` She takes a brush out of a drawer and quietly brushes her hair for a few minutes. `&'Well, guess if you want things done...'``
Ethera grabs a pen and a tablet of paper and writes a letter.
`^Mom.'``
`^Sorry to do this on such short notice, but the bussiness is having a few problems that need my attending to. I'm headed to L.A. immediatly. Not sure when i'll be back, 'cause this is pretty serious.``
`^I'll have my phone on me if i'm needed. Do me a favor and don't get yourself killed or hurt while i'm away, ok? That'd be a bummer total.``
`^Always remember that i'm your daughter, always have been and will be.``
`^Love always...   Eth'ra Yamazaki``


She reads over the letter then begins to write another. `^Rinako...``
`^You asked me not to leave, and I didn't. Sorry I can't do the same this time. It's bussiness...and sort of personal.
`^Anyway, to cut to the chase, I need to take care of this bussiness problem, and while I do that, look at my options.
`^I love you, Rina. More than I could ever say, show or buy. You're a trusted friend, lover and someone who i'd love to spend the rest of my life with, however long that lasts.
`^But..there are a few things you need to know. Sorry I can't tell you in person. Just a cowardly bitch, I guess.
`^My past, recent past, i'd never talked to you about. I was abused, Rina. Mentally, physically, sexually...You..scared me once. I know you didn't mean to. You never knew, and that's my fault.
`^Plus...I've been thinking, Rina. I want a child. Wish you and I could have one. After we are married, of course. Assuming you still want me after this letter.
She stops and sighs..`&'Eth'ra Amatsu-Kirogami...'`` She goes back to her letter.
`^Please trust in me while i'm gone. I'm sorry, and, it's me, not you. I just need to think things over.``
Crying lightly, Ethera reads over the letter before signing it. `^Forever yours....Eth'ra Amatsu-Kirogami``


`^P.S.  Would you be willing to take me flying when I get back?``
~
