Sir Tyronos,

You will have to excuse the sloppy writing Sir, but my arm seems to be convulsing.  I have
not been doing well, I have recently inhereted some hallucinations and the like from a former
'resident' in my body.  I can write this now steadily enough...the lapses in sanity seem to come
at innopportune and unpredictable times, and this is the reason I write you.

I can't allow my problems to affect you, or Kuami, or the others, and I can't allow myself
to endanger anyone's lives with my instability.  I have made preparations for myself to be
commited into an asylum, therefor ridding you of any problems or burdens I might cause.

I have been watching the boy that delivered this message to you for some time now, he seems to
be some kind of oracle or prophet or something.  I have arranged so that he delivers this note
to you in the hopes that he can be of some assistance in my absence.  My apologies again for
this, and may God grant me the sanity to return soon.

Barius Zoana

OOC: In character, Barius has already gone away, so he couldn't participate in this quest.  Bryson
will serve as his substitute if its ok, i've been looking for a way to integrate him anyway.
