`&'Hey, i'm going to Ireland. See the sights, get away from the strangness of this city...and to collect my thoughts. Not sure when i'll be back. I'll   have my phone and pager if you need me. Love ya, Eth.'``



As Rinako wakes up, there's a letter on the dresser adressed to her and a dozen white roses. It's in Eth's  handwriting.
