Subject YES!~
Text
Sirus runs down the street with his hands in the air, making a wooshing
sound.  Soon he finds Nomyuki, by cooincidence.

Sirus: "Hey!  Uh... due to... err... circumstances, it's all part of my
plan of course, you have now been promoted to leader of Jurai!"

Nomyuki: "Really?  KEEN!"

Sirus: "Ke...KEEN!?  No no no!  You're the leader now, you have to 
answer with your family's HONOR!  And PRIDE!  I swore to my father's
latin lover's grave that I would NEVER let Jurai be disgraced as such!"

Nomyuki: "....Oh.  Uh, okay.   ...By my father's... wooden leg?"

Sirus: "...It's a start.  Oh yeah, and here's your discount card.  You
get 10% off at Macy's."

Nomyuki "WOW!  I suddenly feel like that is a popular discount, or 
something!  Almost like it's been used many, MANY times before!"

Sirus: "What?"

Nomyuki: "...What?"

-----------------------------Meanwhile...------------------
Suzuran hikes up his skirt and slides another pizza into Althena's
mouth, with a large pizza spatula, and wipes the sweat from his brow.

Suzuran: "...God, my life is great!"

Althena: "Ming-cha la POONKA, King TWINKIE-DA!!"

------------------*shudder*  Uh, I mean, "Meanwhile..."----
Argyle suddenly looks over his shoulder... seeing nothing, and returning
to his normal stance, before suddenly jerking over and looking again.

Argyle: "...I swear, it must be getting close to St. Patrick's day or
something..."

Meanwhile, Ruka spies on Argyle, invisibly, at the area he keeps looking
at, but seeing nothing, confusedly.

Ruka: "Yeah, that's right, LOOK at me you little bitch.  Yeah.  Yeah...
just you wait, I got JUST the job for you... I wanna see your DP, baby!"

Argyle suddenly jerks his head around again, sighs, and looks back, to
see Ruka's face, point blank.

Ruka: "Hi."

Argyle: "AAAHHHHH!!! ..." *gets over the surprise, and see's it's Ruka*
"...AAAHHHH!"

Ruka: "Enough, enough!  Listen up, honeybuns, I need you to find 
Tasselhoff."

Argyle: "What?  Him?  Why?  And why me?"

Ruka: "Because you're the strongest schnookims I know!" *rubs his thigh*
"Pleeease?"

Argyle: "Alright, alright!  Just don't do that again..."

Argyle begins to walk off, and pauses for a moment.

Argyle: "Ever.                     ...Ever."

-----I'm becoming afraid to say it again, but... "Meanwhile..."---
Akaru stands in Pizza hut, with goggle eyes and a vacant open-mouthed
smile, not moving an inch while Suzuran suddenly appears, grabs a pizza, 
and dissappears again.

Akaru: "... @.X"

Akaru suddenly farts, but still doesn't move.

Akaru: "I don't know why I'm here... Spadoinkle..."

TO BE CONTINUED!
~
