Subject DYYYYNAMIC!~
Text
Late at the RP bar, flashing lights advertise the news that a live band is
going to be preforming, tonight.  Boasting an undisclosed name, people visit
in curiosity as to who it could be.

Like moths to a flame, the New Kansas bar is filled with unknowing customers
as the wooden floor creaks, not quite accustomed to more then 3 people, let
alone the hefty audience that was building up.  Luckily, after certian 
unmentionable heavyweights rocked the RP scene, support columns were
installed, littered all over the basement level.  The front row, closest to
the stage, is lined with gold-plated seats, meant for the immortals.

Vimes: "Dees bedder be weert it, main, It's no easy running de border, esse!
I CUT MY SHURRT, MAIN!"

Suzuran: "Does this dress make me look fat?"

Fatetaf: "Aaah... no..."

Batanen: "Does this power ranger outfit make me look fat?"

Fatetaf: "Uhhh.... No."

Althena: "How about me?  Does this dress make me look fat?"

Fatetaf: "Of course not!  *coughyour FAT makes you look fatcough*"

Althena: "What?"

Fatetaf: "I said... uhh... Your cat makes jewish cook-offs?"

Althena: "Cook-off... I'm hungry."

Suzuran: "OOoh, I KNEW I should have went for the pink one with the frills!"

Fatetaf: "I feel like I'm sitting at the special ed table..."

Vimes: "JOOO WANT A TAAACOOO, MAAAANNN!?"
-----------------
Outside, people line the block, waiting to get in.  Mainly because 
there's a megazord double-parked in front of the bar.  The Bouncer looks at 
his watch, and sees it's finally time to start letting people in.

Seitzer: "Okay, who's first?"

Seitzer starts checking ID, and letting people on through.  Only a handful
of people get in, before--

Desh: "YOU'RE the bouncer!?"

Seitzer: "Sho nuff."

Desh: "Psh." *looks at his date* "Can you believe this!?"

Seitzer: "......Nope.  Next?"

Desh: "WHAAAT!?  Hey, c'mon, this is gee golly silly!  Let me in!  Don't 
embarass me in front of my date!  It took an hour of convincing to make my 
sister come!  Look at this facial hair, I shave almost every WEEK!"

Seitzer: "Where?"

Desh: "LOOK CLOSER!"

Seitzer: ".... still don't see it.  Next?"

Desh: "ARRGH! I don't have to take this, I'm going in!"

Desh walks by Seitzer, and Seitzer doesn't even try to stop him.  Suddenly, 
Desh dissappears in a poof of smoke.  Someone should have told him it 
