back.  The lights raise, and a band is on stage.  'Bishop' is written on a 
turntable...

All of a sudden, a big black man kind of runs, kind of skips in a dancy way 
onto stage, as the pyrotechnics go off.

Sirus: "Sonic...   SSYYYYYYYYyyyYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYIIIIIIIDDDEEEE!!  CAN 
YOU FEEEEEEELLLLL THIIIIIIIIISSSSS!!!???"

The crowd is completely silent (lost) as a band runs on stage, and Sirus 
stomps back and forth, bopping his head in the direction of each step.

Sirus: "CAN YOU FEEL IIIIIT!?"

The turntable starts thumping out a deep bass beat, and Sirus starts wailing
on a guitar and rapping about sonic related matters, women, being black and
his bulbouse, black genitals.  

About halfway through Akaru runs out screaming into a microphone, not making
sense, and Sirus starts wailing on the guitar even harder and more 
pyrotechnics go off.  A giant pig floats down from the ceiling and water 
bottles fly through the air somehow, without having any obvious origin. 
Suddenly, Nyro floats down on a cable spouting Nyroglyphics and making even
less sense then Akaru.

Nyro: "ROK TEH HUOSES!  I AM TEH COOL!  MY NIGAGS!"

As Nero's cable get jammed, and he gets stuck like a Middle School Peter-Pan
play, as Akaru tries to crowd surf, jumping off the stage and smacking into
the floor.  Then, all of a sudden (EVERYTHING here is of a sudden!) the beat 
seamlessly changes to a tinkling, ice-cream truck like melody.

Voice: "FAYGO BREAK!"

Seitzer skips onto stage with a big ol' bucket and black and white clown 
makeup, and splashes the entire audience with a wave of cheap soda.

The beat continues, and Sirus gets more extreme, rapping about stereophonics
and tappin some certian posteriour.  This continues for an hour or so more, 
before the beat fades out, and everyone on stage gives shout-outs to people
nobody's ever heard of before, and leaves.

Time it took for the audience to recover from inital shock?  Twenty minutes 
after the show ended.

Time it took for the audience to recover completely?  A lifetime.

THE END
