Subject Writing Quest~
Text
`UTetsuo Shima``
``   In some respects, I've always had a connection with his kid. I was taunted when I was small
because of how little and weak I was. I had few friends, and those I did have seemed quite abusive
towards me. And had I attained the kind of power that Tetsuo, I most likely would have used them
to lash out against the world I hated so dearly. Thankfully, I have grown out of much of the anger
I had for those around me. I found real friends to rely on, and a way to accept things as they
were. Yet, there is always a hint of paranoia and rage which haunts me when threatened.
(Tetsuo, from the movie: AKIRA)

`USpike``
``      He's got my kind of agenda; indifferent everything and everyone except for what will affect him 
directly. Spike likes to cut through most of the shit and get to what's important. Most of the time,
I'm like that, if I feel like something needs to get solved RIGHT now, which is how I feel about most
everything. And Spike, like me, will do anything to benefit himself, even if it is 'the smallest of
the small fries'.
(Spike, from the series: Cowboy Bebop)

`UTaikoubou``
``   Now this is a guy I really can relate to. Sleepin' when he should be doin his work, and putting
everything off to the last minute. Even then, he has to put everything on the line in one huge
project that may forgive all the laziness that he's done. Even then, his effort is minimal, but
when his mind is put to it, everything comes together wonderfully. Always cynical and crafty,
his friends think he's just being a bum as usual, but he's sure of the plan that he's hatching in
that mind of his will solve all his problems. I have to say, out of all the anime characters I've 
seen, this guy comes closest to what I'm like. Hell, if I put on some funny clothes, we'd even look 
similar! *Looks at self* Oh, wait...
(Taikoubou from the `Umanga``: Houshin Engi)


---Tyronos
~
