Subject tall, dark stranger~
Text
As the news report (from the previous rpnote of Rujin's) ended, a strange dark man finished his drink in a cafe, watching it on the TV above the counter and frowning.
(`6What troubled times I've woken in.``) he thought. Standing and pulling a wide brimmed hat over his head, hiding his pale face in shadow, he walked out into the night.
(`6These pathetic things of the night profane our once noble image.``) He shook his head and looked up to the moon as if expecting to find something there. (`6It would seem that I've slept for far too long...``)
Fingering his rapier under his cloak, he walked off, on a mission to reclaim the night. (`6I think my first order of buisness shall be to kill this...thing which is stalking people and slaughtering them.``)
He shook his head again and sighed. "`12000 years.....``"
(`6I've been away for too long...``)
~
