Text
Night falls once more on Neo-Toyko, and the creatures that dwell in it emerge once more.
Serith sighs slightly and looks around. Ever since that news broadcast, and the emergence of `!V`1ampire `&H`8unter``
he, and all the others like him have had to be a bit more careful about where to get their meals.

`^Where to hunt tonight... I suppose I'll just stick close to my haven.`7

He looks around and walks out into the night, relishing the cool air. The scent of life fills his 
nostrils and he breathes it deeply. 
`^Someone is close.`7 He moves quietly around the corner only to find an unsuspecting victim waiting for him.
He leaps to attack, quickly sinking his fangs into his victim. As the victim struggles and fights, Serith is
thrown from his meal, only to watch him flee into the night.

