Text
`&***************************************************``

`&A`7n`&i`7m`&e`7M`&U`7D `&R`7ole`8-`&P`7laying `6Q`^u`&e`^s`6t``

What this quest would happen to be a is quest open to
anyone who wants to Role Play in a large scale adventure.
What I hope will happen is people will intergrate their
characters into the game and come out with new alliances
and enemies to take to them to PK, Questing, or what have
you. Only apply if you are seriously interested.

How this will work is people will apply to me with their RP
or even PK alts, and I'll place them into a scenerio. There
will then be an entire Rp document written up to give focus
to all factions of the involved parties. RP will then commence
on a stricted day and/or place(s), followed by quests or any
other type of activity that will move the story along.

`&Example:`` There is a heated election going on to elect a new
president of Neo-Tokyo. There will be two people who are the
candidates, a faction of people who work for them to keep them
safe, and another faction who are investors in the candidates
who might send assassins, etc, after the candidates.

`&Example 2:`` Peace treadies are going on within City X's walls
to allow free access by anyone of any race. These treadies and
laws are enforced by heroes or magical girls, etc. One of the
main city heads is a total bigot who owns a mercanary camp 
and will loose billions if outsiders are allowed to trade
within city limits, hences, a small civil war might break out.

Keep in mind that the whole point of this quest is not combat,
or killing or fighting. It'll try and be a small dynamic part of
the MUD what will breathe by itself.

`&Goals:``

So, what's in it for you all? Good role playing, I hope, for one.
But, after the focus document is written out, anyone in the
quest will have goals to meet. For everyone of those goals met on
a weekly basis, you and your faction will be rewarded with points.
Not RP Points, but tallied points in this quest which can buy goods.
Equipment, mostly, but restrings as well.

`&To Apply:``

Write an `&RP note`` to `&Sirus`` and give me the `&listed`` information.

`&Name:``
`&Character Descrpition:`` Disposition, occupation, alignment, goals, etc, etc.
`&Physical Appearance:`` What does s/he look like? Carry him/herself? Clothes?
`&Important Errata:`` Weapon favorism? Hatreds? Background info? Whatever.

Alright then, if you are interested, let me know.
Sirus.

`&***************************************************``
~
