Subject The stuff that `8n`7i`8ghtmares ``are made of.~
Text
``  Darkness.  Everything black.  Sure, it's a theme way overused, but
I can't just lie and say I saw everything.  The whole dream was black.
It was horrible.  The stuff nightmares are really made of.  Looking
back now, I don't even want to remember...but it just feels too
important for me to look over.

``  I may not have been able to see anything, but I could certainly
recognize my own voice.  "`^Why won't my magic work!  You just...you
can't just die now..you can't``!"

``  But the voice which responded was none that I had heard before.
"`2Ikern!  Get it together, this fight's not over yet!  We're counting
on you!``"

``  "`^But she's hurt!  Maybe even dead...I can't leave her like this!``'
I shouted at the voice in protest.

``  "`2We're ALL gonna die if you don't get with it!``"  And then there was
that scream.  That scream that tells me that it was the last time he
would ever scream.  And then there was another scream.  It was a girl's
scream, and an unfamiliar one.  But I'd never know, because it was her
last too.  Somehow, I felt alone.  Cold, too.  That was the last thing
I felt...

``  Awake.  The sweet release of the morning had come.  I couldn't help
but wonder who those people were...those people who died right in front
of me, and I never saw their faces.

--`@R`#P`6D`^a`6n``
~
