Satan's testicles sure have a knack for surprises.
I took the head and cradled it in my arms.
It was like a small child.
I planted it in the ground. Maybe it'll grow.

I think the vamp will look better with that pretty cut down his face.
Immortals heal pretty quickly, I suppose.
So it'll be gone before anyone notices.
They'll think it's a shaving cut.

Serith didn't smell like an old one.
Maybe he will be, some day.
