Text
At the shinto temple, two familiar faces stand here.

Ruka : So, I hear Fatetaf is running a new weapons quest.

Legis : I'd run right through hell and back.

Ruka : Right. You know Will, I was really thinking that I could get this neat spear. Now that I'm a hero.

Legis : And I'll never forget the way you feel right now. Oh no, no way.

Ruka : Right. And I was thinking that...
Legis : I would do anything for love, and that's a fact.

Ruka : I think now that it's come to a term in our relationship where we can stop everquesting.

Legis suddenly frowns.

Legis : I would do anything for love, but I won't do that. No I won't do that.

Suddenly, a guitar solo flashes, along with a drum beat!

Legis suddenly starts singing!

Legis : Oh I would do anything for love. Oh I would do anything for love, but I won't do that!

Legis : And some days autoquest don't come easy!

Legis : And some days it don't come hard!

Legis : And some days it come at all and these are the days you never log on!

Legis : And sometimes you're firebreathed! And some night's your poisoned and hasted!

Ruka : Will... I was just thinking that we could spend more time together or on mud or something.

Legis : As long as the planets are turning! As long as the stars are burning!

Legis : As long as your dreams are coming through, you better believe it!

Legis : I would do anything for love, but I won't give up everquest.

The drum beat and guitar seem to fade out.

Ruka : .... Are you done?

Legis : Yeah.

Kevin quickly runs up to the two of them.

Kevin : Hey ruka, hey legis! Guess what I got?

Both of them turn to the man in the trench coat.

Ruka : What is it?

Kevin pulls out a jar from his coat.
Inside the jar, is a small bug.

Legis : What is that?

Kevin : I proved myself! I caught the bug all by myself! It was my idea! I didn't have help!

Ruka : Weren't you with Sirus?

Kevin : well... ummm... yeah, he helped a little. But I did it all by myself! I caught the bug!

--flashback--

Sirus and Kevin stand in a field. There's flowers and a lot of bugs around.

Sirus : You see, my brave friend, the knight Kevin, before you catch the bug you must vow.

Kevin : Vow? How do I do that?

Sirus's eyes light up at the prospect of a new student.

Sirus : First, you swear! I recommend your half-brother's uncle's cousin's sister's daughter's honor.

Kevin : oh ok, right right.

--flashback ends--

Kevin : I caught the bug all by myself, I'm a real coder now!

Ruka : That's great.

Legis : Rock and roll dreams come true!

Suddenly, a large tremor shakes the ground and the three fall to thier knees.

After a few moments the tremor ends.

Ruka : What was that?

Legis : Life is a lemon and I want my money back!

Kevin : I am not sure. But by my goldfish's sister's half-cousin's diplomacy, I'll avenge him!

Sirus pops his head out of Kevin's trench coat.

Sirus : That's good for a beginner, but I learned much faster. After all, I am of noble blood and I have won countless victories throughout the galactic universe. I am equalled by none.

Ruka : I think we should really investigate that earthquake.

Kevin : I'll bring my net! We can catch bugs!

Sirus hops out of Kevin's trench coat.

Sirus : well, this looks like a job for ex-jurai, current immortal, Sirus Sonic knight! After all, without such a profound group leader as myself you would all be lose.

So the four head to the underground, underdark, to investigate the tremor. What lies there? Who knows.

Elsewhere.

Akaru : My plans! muwahahha! Yes! You fruity ass! My plans are almost complete! Soon, my diabolic machine Bongzilla will be rebuilt!

-To be continued-
~
