To      all~
Subject GASP!~
Text
Aeron stands there holding her neck, blinking several times.
The crimson colored liquid flows from the small wound upon her neck,
through her fingers and down her wrist.  She closes her eyes slowly and
quietly sheds a tear or two.  Though mostly painless, the small
gash burns ever so slightly as she removes her hand.  Aeron stares
at her hand, blood covering it from fingertips to palm, and rips a
small strip of cloth from her shroud.  She ties it carefully around
her neck, trying to put pressure upon the scrape that she had endured.

Aeron thinks to herself, '`6How.. could this have happened..?  All``
`6training, countless battles.. just to end in a few seconds...?!``'

She touches her bandaged neck, tracing the wound with her fingertip.

'`6Seems to be.. nothing more than a scratch, rather than a bite.  Hmm.``'  she
ponders, while examining herself.

She looks around the nearby vicinity, looking for the ghastly creature
that had harmed her.  Nothing, but the sound of the wind comforting her.

'`6He could have .. killed me.  Or even worse, turned me.``'  She shudders momentarily,
trying to relax.  She resheathes both of her swords and peers around herself,
looking for any traces of Rujin and the others.

'`6I must find Rujin.. He's the only reason I'm.. ``'  she quickly looks up,
a very quiet, almost infrasonic, sound pulse is coming from the space about
twenty or thirty feet from her.  She stares in the direction of the noise for a
few moments, watching.  A small speck of light shines then dissipates.  Aeron
raises her eyebrow and curses loudly.

'`^GAH!  Those fuckers got Rujin!  Son of a.. ``'  with that she leaps down from
the building, standing before the spot where she had saw the light.

'`6They must have used a magical portal or nexus.  Perhaps I can follow the same path``
`6if I hurry.``'  She waves her left hand in the suspected spot and recites a spell,
opening a small gate, to what she hopes will lead her to Rujin.
She gets ready to leap through the portal and then pauses right before
entering.  She stares at the opalesque gate swirling before her, thinking.

'`6Why.. did they take Rujin?  Who are these men after him?!  And what does this``
`6Serith fellow have to do with it all.``  She looks around herself one last time,
making sure the hellspawn isn't near and then leaps into the portal, praying
for safe travel....


`1Aer`!o`1n`&--  `8The place that you have come to `1f`!e`1ar `8the most..``
~
