Character Description: My occupation is a wanderer. I go around from place to place helping anyone in need, within reason of course. My alignment is good. I'm usually nice and friendly and easy to get along with.

Description: 5'10, female, wears a white shirt and long jeans. She looks like any normal teenage of the real world. She tries her best to fin it. She's 18 years old. She not very pretty but not ugly.

Other stuff: She likes using exotic weapons but if she can't find those, a dagger will do. Her favorite weapon is a Crescent Moon wand. Her backup is the Power of Planet Mars. She hates when people pick on others the most.
