Background: Saiyan Mages are hard to come by. She's been taught in the ways of the mage at a young age. Her parents told her it was unless, but she persisted. With her spells she's helped many people. 
Her parents told her if she went through with her mage training, she would never be able to come back home. Her parents wanted her to become a fighter like all decent Saiyan's, but she refused saying that's not the way she wanted to be. 
So she left home, and hasn't been back since. She misses her home and her parents... but she knew she did the right thing. She's determined to make her parents proud of her and one day comes home.

I know this note sucksbut I'm a much better Rper than I am on writing background on my character.

