Text
Akaru : Nyaha, skittle butt-plug terminators! My creation!

Akaru stands before a gigantic drilling machine, in the center of underdark.

Akaru : Aunt jemima pancakes! Hurry up with the spadoinkling! We are almost there!

The earth shakes violently as the drill burrows deeper and deeper, harder and deeper. Slowly then faster, harder and deeper.

Akaru : Nya ha ha! This is like mud sex!

Ruka, Sirus, Kevin and Legis walk into the room.

Ruka : I knew akaru was behind this!

Legis : No I won't do that.

Akaru quickly flicks a switch on the drill and it turns off.

Sirus : What are you doing with this giant machine?

Akaru : Ahhh... `@@`7.`8x`7 nothing!

Legis : I would do anything for love, but I won't do that.

Ruka : It looked like you were drilling into the ground and causing earthquakes!

Akaru pulls out a mop from behind his back.

Akaru :  AAhhhH I didnt do it!  Did I do it?  NO I DIDNT!  Everyone who did it, raise your hands! 

Akaru runs away.

The four stand there for a moment then look at each other, then the drill.
Sirus pushes the three out of the way.

Sirus : I know what I must do! I shall destroy the evil contraption and avenge my brother's sister mother's grandma's apple pie's honor!

Sirus : But first, I need a decent opponent! En guarde senior drill!

Sirus flicks the drill's switch on.

The drill activates, except now twice as fast and twice as hard and deeper.

Kevin : I don't think you should have done that?

Sirus : Silence my wannabe juraian!

Sirus : I know what I'm doing, so step aside!

Sirus pushes Kevin down, who falls on his rear.

Sirus : Now, Senior Drill, have at you!

Sirus places his hand on his sword hilt. He then does several backflips, stands on one hand then begins breakdancing.

Sirus : Now, feel my blade!

Sirus quickly draws his sword and slashes at the drill.
With a loud clunk, his sword shatters into pieces and tears swell into his eyes.

Sirus : what... no... how could this?

Sirus begins to cry. And cry he does, like a little sissy!

Ruka : Sirus, I think that we better get out of here!

A spotlight suddenly flashes onto legis and he begins singing.

Ruka : No! Will! We don't have time for a musical number!

Legis : ohhhhh, rock and roll dreams come trueeee!

Sirus : I don't think we can stop him Ruka!

Ruka : No.... one thing can. I am pained to have to use this.

Legis : Rock and roll dreams come through!

Ruka : Legis, hurry, I need 5 bone chips and ten bat wings!

Legis's eyes light up and he hops around like a little kid.
Legis quickly turns towards the underdark entrance and begins running.

Sirus and Ruka turn to each other, and turn to the drill which is starting to smoke.
They quickly bolt towards the entrance.

Kevin finally, in his big heavy trenchcoat manages to stand up.
Kevin pulls a bug net out from his cloak.

Akaru quickly decends from the ceiling with his mop.

Akaru : Nya ha ha ha! You fruity ass! I won't let you stop the reincarnation of bongzilla!

Kevin wipes his nose with his long sleeve.

(Who will win the fight between kevin and akaru?!)
(Who ever thought these two would face off?!)

Stay tuned!
~
