Subject Waking from a Nightmare, Into Hell pt. 1~
Text
Rujin finally awoke, lying on a thin bed in a room that resembled a jail cell. He
couldn't determine the time consciousness strayed from him, but it must have been
awhile. Waking up in a cell didn't suprise Rujin, he figured he was either going
to end up in jail or never wake up at all. That man who took him, Botiden? Botolen?
He couldn't remember, that man insisted he knew Rujin, yet Rujin had no idea who
or what the man was. Some of his shrouds had been torn, and his head swam in a sea
of dizziness and pain. That Bot-something or other guy had hit him pretty hard. 
Though he remembered Serith, and his defiance against his own race, and his own needs.
Rujin began to question if this course of action he had taken was the best path to
become that thing that really old, nice vampire told him about. Rujin gripped the
sides of his head angrily, memories of violence, hatred, hunger, pain, all replaying
themselves to him quickly, and non-sensically. Thats when Rujin heard a voice in
his head, or he thought it was in his head.

`8Demonic Voice `1'`!Heh, heh, heh, well it seems we are well met again, Skyrender`1'``

Rujin looked around him quickly, searching for the voice, it frightened him greatly
but sounded familiar.

Rujin frantically whispered '`^Who's there? Are you in my head?``'

`8Demonic Voice `1'`!No, Skyrender, I am very real. It seems you have a slight``
`!case of amnesia. No matter, I can cure that for you.`1'``

Out of the shadows on the far side of the room from Rujin came a beast the young
vampire remembered well from his nightmares. Tall, blood red skin wrapped around
immense muscles. The thing was built like an ox, It's fingers ending with not 
fingernails but talons that were black as jet. The lower half of it's body clothed
in a huge legged pants made of a shimmering black fabric. Protruding from beneath
the pants when it walked were taloned toes like an eagle from Hell. Wings lay folded
across his back, huge, wrapped in a thin layer of leathery, red skin. Atop his bald
head came two horns from right above his forehead, arcing up enough to touch the
ceiling of this cell, then descending down almost to meet the junction of his wings
to his body. But none of this was as frightening, not even his mouth filled with
small, razor sharp teeth, it was the thing's eyes. Slighty sunken in, dragon like
and blazing red.

Rujin scrambled against the wall trying to escape '`^Who the hell are you?!``'

The huge Demonic Creature stepped forward grinning broadly. It continued to get closer
until it reached the bed, then leaned down staring Rujin right in the face. The young 
vampire pressed against the wall frightened, the feeling of impending death over
came him.

`8Kaoseraph chuckled `1'`!I am Kaoseraph.`1'``

`1R`!u`#j`!i`1n `8- `6'`^When your ripe you'll bleed out of control`6'``
~
Sender  Rujin~
Date    Sun Jun 23 11:56:17 2002~
