To      all~
Subject Poem~
Text
There once was a newbie
All fresh and all new
He walked around aimlessly
No sure what to do
But to his relief
He saw a small sign
That would surely fix all of his problems in time
The sign that he read,
Though it wasn't well written,
Said "What would you do if you had ever been bitten?"
The newbie was confused, as you can see plainly
As he looked at this sign very strangely

Then something else seemed to catch his fancy
A big sign that said "Nudity and dancing"
A big grin appeared on his face
And read the rest of the sign on the vase
"Just gate to Pazzi and walk a few south"
"And soon you too will be nude and be dancing"
That's just what he fancies

He gated to Pazzi and went a few south
Where there he met Satan, the great big turd
And killed him before he could utter a word
He was dead as a doornail
His brains at his feet
He woke up at the Alter, all bloody and beat
Naked as can be
He let out a scream
And danced madly about the room for all to see
So the sign was true
Because now he was nude and dancing too

Now let this be a warning
To all that are new
Beware of the signs
And the big turd too
~
