Subject The esper pirate!~
Text
Sit ye down and grab a cup of the finest ale
Whilst I tell you of the pirates tale
Way before the Kenshin clan
There was a pirate who sailed the lands
Drinking his ale and eating his cheese
He sailed for booty across the 7 seas

Then one day the pirate fell
over the bellows and into a well.
As he woke he heard a sound
"Tis a monster with a red aura, rising from the ground!"

With all his might he did slay the beast
and turned him into a wonderus feast!
After the meal his eyes did blaze
his skin now took an esper glaze!

Back to Neo-tokyo with his new power
He drank and drank, hour after hour.
He created roses, and stupid flowers
then decided to make some rper's cower.

Back to Kansas, from which he was banished
He wanted to make the rest of them vanish
He knocked down the door with and with all of his might
screamed "Merry christmas to all, and to all a goodnight!"

Then he was slain and newbanned.

We miss you esper Pirate!!
~
