The old and tired monk has risen again
He has been sent on a Quest by the mighty Lord Fatetaf
His mission is to bring Honor back to the Clones who he has somehow come to lead
With his newest clones fleeing for refuge in the mighty Shenshin-Gumi the battle falls on his shoulders
He spots the Vampire Nomyuki, trained in the art of magic, and gives chase
The Mighty Zeitgeist summons balls of holy light and sends them hurling at this demonic creature
The Vampire squirms in agony and tries to flee from the battle
The old and tired monk can not seem to walk fast enough so he has to relay on his unreliable teleporting skills
He yearns to come face to face with this mage again and over and over he teleports around until he finally meets this Vampire
He mutters something then throws his fist at the Vampire sending him hurling in the air
The Mage again tries to flee but this time the monk is fast enough 
As the holy light falls upon the Mage he falls do the ground, his flesh on fire
The mighty clones seem to be back, ready to handle any obstacles

(ooc) Fight x2
(ooc) Zeit-2 Nomy-0
Invid=2
Kenshin-Gumi=-2
