Subject Watching~
Text
Kaeka sits on the curb across the street from Erik's office, sighing.
'Everything I remember...it brings me back here....was this place important for Mother and Father...?' she thinks...
She looks up at the tall building, wondering....'Mabey there was something here at one time? I had to have been here...' she sighs again...
Stands in the darkness, looking up and down Clan Road. She smiles slightly to herself....'Well....at least I know the trees in the park are my home...'
Smiling, she walks down Clan Street, making her way to the park in the center of town...
~
