Subject `8The first patr`&o`8l.``~
Text
`8After shadowmelding in the dusk, Sehnzseighet began his first hunter patrol.
Too bad he was too young and unexperienced to hear or sense `!D`1unp`!e`1al `&H`8unter's
flappings following by far the same trail as Sehnzseighet was.

It was particularly cold that night, and Sehnzseighet hands' fire was
growing slowly, almost fading.

He was calmer and could think before acting this time. He went down the
town but nothing abnormal happened so far.

Sehnzseighet walked through the small city, he met some villagers,
adventurers, guards. But one took more of his time, atention and power:


`7Sehnzseighet: `8'`^Good night.`8'

`&A`7d`&v`2e`@n`7t`&u`7r`@e`2r`8: `8'`^Sup new comer.`8'

`7Sehnzseighet: `8'`^I have just arrived town.`8'

`&A`7d`&v`2e`@n`7t`&u`7r`@e`2r`8: `8'`^I have noticed, be careful thou. Opportunists are all around,
waiting for you to be weak.`8'

`7Sehnzseighet: `8'`^Thanks for the advice. Actually, I was going for a walk
around just to learn the land.`8'

`&A`7d`&v`2e`@n`7t`&u`7r`@e`2r`8: `8'`^Really? Well, I have just planned a trip around it too, I could
join you, if you want to, of course. I could also teach you some shortcuts
and the main roads to get to other towns and different places.`8'

`7Sehnzseighet: `8'`^Wonderful! I'd love it, thank you so much!`8'

`&A`7d`&v`2e`@n`7t`&u`7r`@e`2r`8: `8'`^Ok, follow me then.`8'


The two walked all around the town chatting, the adventurer also told him
his experiences at wars and challenges. Sehnzseighet surely learnt a lot
from that old fighter.


`&A`7d`&v`2e`@n`7t`&u`7r`@e`2r`8: `8'`^Sorry kid, but you'll have to go back to town by yourself. I
must follow my path to the forest. Elders say there is a great treasure
there, and I'm gonna find out if it is true or not.`8'

`7Sehnzseighet: `8'`^Ok. Thank you so much for the information. I really
appreciate your help.`8'

`&A`7d`&v`2e`@n`7t`&u`7r`@e`2r`8: `8'`^It's no problem I like motivating people who are new here. We
never know when we'll need some assistance.`8'

`7Sehnzseighet: `8'`^Exactly, if you need anything that I can help with, just look
for me, my name is Sehnzseighet.`8'

`&A`7d`&v`2e`@n`7t`&u`7r`@e`2r`8: `8'`^Sehnzseighet, a different name... Well Sehnz-whatever, there is
this creature following us since we left the town, be careful about him.`8'

`7Sehnzseighet: `8'`^Ok. I'll look for it. See you around.`8'

`&A`7d`&v`2e`@n`7t`&u`7r`@e`2r`8: `8'`^Good-bye.`8'


Sehnzseighet waited for his newest friend to go on, and when his image was
too far away to be seen Sehnz turned to the other side of the road and
started walking back town and then to the top of the mountain, where the
abandoned factory is.


`7Sehnzseighet: `8'`^Oh.. your still there?!`8'

`!D`1unp`!e`1al `&H`8unter: `8'`^Yes. How was your first patrol?`8'

`7Sehnzseighet: `8'`^Peaceful I'd say. I've met a few townspeople, one of them
even took me on a little trip with him.`8'

`!D`1unp`!e`1al `&H`8unter: `8'`^Good. He is a nice guy I know him.`8'


The young looked at his older friend demanding an explanation.

`!D`1unp`!e`1al `&H`8unter: `8'`^I have followed you on your walk. I don't let my new
members walk around alone like that.`8'

Sehnzseighet was amazed and then he remembered:

`7Sehnzseighet: `8'`^Oh.. you were the creature he was talking about...`8'

`!D`1unp`!e`1al `&H`8unter: `8'`^Yeap. I couldn't hide from him, he is a `&w`7a`&r `2v`@e`7t`&e`7r`@a`2n`^.`8'

`7Sehnzseighet: `8'`^I've listened his stories, he seem good.`8'

By that time, the full moon wasn't even up in the sky anymore. And the first
rays of light started to lighten up the day. After a long night, it was time
to rest.``
~
