Subject `!V```1amp```!i```1re`` `&H```8unter`` vs `8Hu```7nte```8r```#-```!W```1arr```!i```1or``~
Text
Atop a high building in Tokyo, Xanretsu stands gazing into the full moon.
With many thoughts crossing his mind, only one satisfies him at the moment.
Flying down the building, he says to himself "`1Time to hunt.``"
Flying into the Temple of Quests, Kreno sat awaiting a challenge.
As soon as the Hunter steps in, Kreno challenges him to a duel.
There was also another Hunter currently present, Kamali, the new Hunter.
Kreno had first asked Kamali to duel, when he refused, he turned to Xanretsu.
Xanretsu agrees, and spells up, hinting Kamali to watch his back
incase "somebody else" wanted to jump in.




Ready and willing, Xanretsu proceeds south of the Healer
in search for Kreno, who was around town awaiting his arrival.
As soon as Xanretsu enters The Common Square, things heat up.
A few rounds of battle and already Kreno was fleeing.
Barely hurt the Hunter proceeds to a safe room to heal up what little damage Kreno inflicted.
After healing, `!D```1unp```!e```1al`` gives Xanretsu the heads up
that Moxi has just came on, a former Hunter-Warrior.
Right after he gets word, Xanretsu proceeds back to Common Square.
As soon as he arrives, Moxi jumps him, and Kamali jumps in to help Xanretsu.
Not long after, Moxi falls to the ground, dead, Xanretsu getting the kill.
As Xanretsu quickly runs to safe, Kreno jumps Kamali.
Xanretsu was blind and couldnt see and was low on health. He had no choice
but to flee. Shortly after healing up, Kamali is dead.
Enraged by what has happend. Xanretsu quickly proceeds to where Kamali
has fallen and attacks Kreno. And after a few rounds and some fleeing,
Xanretsu finishes Kreno in the Market Square.



`!V```1amp```!i```1re`` `&H```8unter`` vs `8Hu```7nte```8r```#-```!W```1arr```!i```1or``, 1-1
~
