Subject `6A`^e`&g`^i`6s `8I`7n`&n``~
Text
Years ago, it was destoryed. A loyal, small Inn devoted to the care
of the local legends who would come to swap stories, get information,
or just plain pick a fight. In one swoop, it was gone. The gods crushed
the building, along with others, in an attempt to control the masses
around the world.

Enter a new age. For the last few monthes, a few brave legends in the
making decided to take a hand up and rebuilt this once pround Inn. And
with that note, the cycle has begun anew. The Aegis Inn stands once more.
With a lack of refuge in these desperate times, sanctuary is rare to find
and this may be the first step in changing that.

-Anonymous

(P.S. 6s,1w,1n)
~
