Subject A new beginning~
Text
`^"When was that again?"``, the drow talked to herself in the loneliness of the bedroom at Aegis Inn: `^"Four years.. it was four years later.. that night I won't forget.."``

The Al'Meyarvri family was small. Only Pirotess' father and mother lived at their farm, since their only daughter went training. It was located in a small village near a cavern that leads to the underground. The peaceful village didn't know, but
this night it would come to it's end. They came out of the cave. Five demons, angry, desiring blood and destruction. The peaceful village was the perfect place to feed them.
It ended quickly. In less than thirty minutes the village was reduced to ashes, right before the drow's eyes. Tears rolled down from Pirotess' face as she looked at her burnt village, her house and.. the dead bodies of her parents.

`^"Yes, I've changed a lot since then.. I have power now, power to end all this madness, power to hunt the devil..."``. She looked at her red fuku shirt, laid down at the bed. `^"Now it begins..."``

Pirotess Al'Meyarvri, `!Dev`1i`!l `8H`7u`&nt`7e`8r``
~
