`&Thomas Reinholder``. (Get the tribute? :P)

``  With a sigh, Kun finishes off his drink in a gulp and sets the glass down lightly.

`8  "`&Daiko, Daiko, Daiko...`8"``, he says to himself, watching the trails of smoke whisp off his cigarette.

``  All in all, it seems the assassin(s) have made their presence quite aware. Or have they? Whichever, the
