To      all~
Subject Kangpeh pt1~
Text
Journal entry 365
What an honor.  I have just been appointed field commander of our majesties calvary troop
I hope to uphold the honour put upon me.
Now if I can only find a way to tell Elenor.
Being sent into the field.  The demons are too close.  I have received my orders.
I told Elenor and she won't speak to me anymore.
After this I'm applying for guard duty.
Journal Entry 366
They have us pinned down.  Sent word for reinforcements but I don't think they'll get here in time
My only wish as that Elenor and the kids will be safe.
Journal Entry 367
We routed them!  They ran before our might.  But there seemed to be more of them last battle.
Journal Entry 368
Heading back to the capital.
Going to stop by hometown and see the kids and Elenor.  I hope that they haven't grown too much.
I hope my lord will honor me with guardianship of my town.
Journal Entry 369
It was all a farce!  I came home to see my beautiful city burned to ashes!
Demons we're dancing in my childrens skin.  I found my wife beaing raped by the demons.
I destroyed them and she died in my arms.  I love you.
Journal Entry 370
we have just gotten to the capital.  My men have been tended to and I have been granted audience with the king tomorrow
I need answers.
Journal Entry 371
This will be last entry I write.  Betrayed!  They gave up my lands to the demons in exchange of the capital
not being harmed!  Hahahahahahahhaha!  They left their subjects to rot!
I quit the service.  I was gonna tell everyone.  My second, Brad, jumped me and left me for dead.
But I came too outside the city walls.  I began to cry and noticed blood out of my eyes.
I accidently swallowed my tears and the oddest thing happened.  I could feel blue flames surrounding my hand.
I accidently burned a tree down with it's power.
Now with this power I shall have my revenge!  On the king, on everyone...especially Erik.  HAHHAHAHA!


Journal found and documented.
Dastinus third chronicolor of the library of Belldandy.
~
Sender  Zefi~
Date    Mon Aug  5 01:37:46 2002~
