To      all~
Subject from the beginning~
Text
Its been a decade now since I left my parents, and Dededo, my home town to seek adventure
out in the world. I've explored many places such as the bermuda triangle. After a few years
I entered the country of transylvania, where i met this man, named Akuma. He offered to give
anything that my heart desired if only i gave him my soul. Naturally this enticing offer
i accepted, i asked for power, strength, and immortality. He transformed me into a
hideous demon. In control of my soul, Akuma ordered me to kill who walk in our path.
We came along my home town, Dededo, and told me to wipe out the city, with the amazing power
he had given me, the powerful spell hellbender. I refused, so Akuma slashed me, whipped me
and tortured me with hellbender. He assasinated my parents and burned my village down.
Near death, Yohko Mano came to me and healed me. She called back my soul to my body, and
regained control. My powers were still intacted, with my soul, i swore to destroy all demons,
I joined up with the Devil Hunters and supplied me with the equipment needed to kill demons.
This is the start of a my new life.
to be continued...
~
