Subject Kun's Bio: The Return!~
Text
I just wanted to resubmit this to you for the website, as I changed a few small details.

Name: Kun
Character Description: Not many know the man, but it's whispered in some circles that he is among the last
of those trained in the old ways of ninja prominent in underground factions in the feudal era of Japan. Even
so, he seems to have adapted to the times of now, using firearms atop the ninja tools of the trade. He is
calm, cool, and collected, even in battle, and tends not to speak unless there is something to be said.
Currently, he is contracted to protect the candidates from harm for an undisclosed sum by a man named Charles
Daiko, leader of the group "Unit-04".
Physical Description: Kun is a caucasian male, standing around 5'10". His medium-sized frame weighs in at a
slim, yet muscular 170 pounds. Crisp ice blue eyes peek from beneath the long bangs of his russet-colored
hair. He can usually be found dressed in a casual business suit, consisting of a black jacket, black pants and
shoes, and a white dress shirt unbuttoned at the collar.
Important Errata: He favors using a combination of his Beretta 92FS semi-automatic pistol, kept in a holster
at the back of his waistline, and a collapseable katana named "Masamune" after the sword of many legends,
hidden in a compartment in the back of his jacket. He has a thing for clove cigarettes, and an unmarked chrome
Zippo is his lightpiece. Other than all this information presented before you now and the stories that are
shared where most ears cannot hear, not much else is publically known about this man, save the fact that he is
quite dangerous in battle, and efficiently gets the job done where others have not.

That should be it. Peace.

`8Kun.``
~
