Subject Application to one of your Quests~
Text
Race:Saiyan 
Class:Warrior
Alignment: Neutral Good
Personality: A bit withdrawn until provoked, then quite outspoken
Age: 534
Background:  Gedion Furymind was born in the Eastern province of Vegita-sei under the full moon. Because of this he has a layer of fur over his body at all times. He was the object of ridacule from his peers for this, and when he became old enou
gh to learn how, he shaved off the hair, and did so again everytime it grew back.

Still the object of ridicule, he left Vegita-sei in search of a place where he could call his own. He landed on Earth a year later, and found a small town in a wood that accepted him for himself, and his personality.

He was usually found venturing into the wood, and on a journey through a new section he met a young man with a shell on his back carrying a large bottle. Asking about the bottle, the young man told Gedion that it was an elixer of agelessness. 
Gedion asked if the young man had already drunken of the bottle, when the man answered in the affermative, Gedion asked to buy the bottle, and did so for 2000 gold. He drank the remainder of the bottle, and when he did he surged with power. 



It has been 500 years since he drank, and that small town he was in evolved into what today is called Neo-Tokyo. No one remembers who he is, and he has become weak through non action.
He must now go and strengthen himself again, for there is a feeling of forboding in his heart.


If this is too outlandish, just tell me, and I will change it.

Gedion Furymind
~
