Subject Translation~
Text
Bryson frowned quietly.  He enjoyed puzzles.  Experience-wise, this had been an easy decryption.
But something was not right...it was almost...all cliches aside, TOO easy.  He hesitated briefly...

Moments later, a message spread across the web directed to anyone who had stolen the transmission in
midflight.  It contained a simple, single line.  '`^Call Me.  5720461`7'``

`4B`$r`&ys`$o`4n 7`- And I ain't laughin...and I ain't jokin anymore...``

(OOC Information: I have a translation.  You want it?  Send me a tell with (5720461) in front of it.
I'll see what I can do for you.  Heh heh...who knows, maybe it'll make a difference between winning
Tima's next quest on a whole.  Bryson out.)
~
