Sender  Sirus~
Date    Sun Sep 29 03:35:09 2002~
Stamp   1033288509
To      all~
Subject The Next Coming...~
Text
The ground is foreign, yet, Sirus charges through the area with
extreme precision, attempting to find his target destination in
a timely manner. Something around here is... wrong. The road in
the street bends around the corner. The knight tilts his head and
presses forward, sliding around the corner on his heel as a small
force hurricane moves him along the ground. Soon, the object of
his chase is in view.

"`^Blazes... What in the world?``" he murmurs to himself as he looks
on at the creature before him. The beastly man stands around 12
feet tall, draped in black leather and spiked armor all over. The
creature was apperently rending the entrails out of a bystander
who happened to be there. The smell of guts and blood surface in
the air, filling the knight's nostrils with a putrid stench. Sirus
looks onward with a look of disgust as he walks up no less then 15
steps from the creature. "`^What the hell are you?``"

"`8The next highest link in the food chain...``" the beast echos in
a sinister tone. "`8...I'm here to take out the universe's mistakes.``"
The large beastly male turned to look Sirus in the eye. The man's
cruel, dulling glowing red eyes seize up and examine the knight.

The knight's body began to tremble under his own aura, which then
flared up into a violent black, swarming with cyan streaks. Sirus
then looked up at the sinister beast, noting the chains and skulls
lining his black leather armor. "`^So... when the universe makes a
mistake, they send in the likes of you? A shame. Figured when the
cosmos makes an accident, they send in something... bigger.``"

"`8Bite your tongue, knight. Before I do. You see... this isn't about
me, or you, or any of us. This world's time has come. Too many of
of the people here have messed up the timeline. Fate isn't to be a
toy for some upstart mortals. Consider me the janitor.``"

Sirus simply narrows his eyes and narrows his blade, looking at the
beast before him. "`^I know... this was all a part of the plan. Now,
let me show you the rest, wretch.``"

***** (OOC: More to come. Watch the the quest) *****
~
