To      Alielle~
Subject Telegram~
Text
Telegram...
To: Alielle
Sender: Ethera
No signature required

Upon further examination, the telegram reads, `^Important, open and read immediatly.``


Once opened, it reads as follows:


`^Dearest Alielle;``
`^There is no easy way to say this, but it needs to be said all the same. STOP``
`^And, though this may seem less sincere, it make it easier for me to say it to your face. STOP``

`^I love you. More than as a friend.  More than as my adoptive-mother-in-law. STOP``

`^Fact of the matter is, I love you in ways no one knows about.  I can't stop thinking about you.``
`^And when I try, I fail.  When I try to think about Shiori, I think of you instead.
`^Don't know if this is what either of us intended, but that's how I feel. STOP``


`^I've been happy with Shiori, but you treat me in a way she never did.  You..you're nice.  We never argue. You're perfect. STOP``


`^The real truth of the matter is, I think i'd be willing to give up everything to be your and yours alone.  I don't think that could would ever happen, though.``
`^I know you wouldn't want to see Shiori hurt, and I can only imagine what my mother would think. STOP.``

`^Maybe i'm just in over my head.  Maybe I don't realy love anyone, just think I do.  I dunno, maybe you could help me figure it out?  Maybe you know someone who could?  STOP``
`^Well, that's all.  Running out of room for this message.  Until next time, I love you dearly. STOP``

Signed,
Ethera.
~
